comments: Thompson (CLE) makes marginal contact with LaVine (CHI) at the end of his drive and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Sexton (CLE) and absorbs the contact.
Garland (CLE) makes marginal contact by brushing Satoransky's (CHI) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Love (CLE) makes marginal contact with Carter Jr. (CHI) and doesn't affect his shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes marginal contact with Sexton (CLE) and doesn't affect his ability to pass.
Porter Jr. (CHI) makes marginal contact with Osman's (CLE) off arm at the start of the drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Young (CHI) establishes a legal guarding position outside of the RA and absorbs the contact as Osman (CHI) drives through his body.
Thompson (CLE) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from LaVine (CHI) during his driving shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (CHI) extends his arm into Clarkson (CLE) and dislodges him during the rebound.
Osman (CLE) briefly engages with Porter Jr. (CHI) on the perimeter and separates without affecting his ability to defend.
Clarkson (CLE) firms up during the off ball screen and makes marginal contact with Young (CHI) that doesn't knock him off his defensive path.
Young (CHI) makes incidental contact to Love's (CLE) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt or ability to follow through naturally.
Thompson (CLE) collapses his left forearm upon contact with Carter Jr. (CHI) as he makes clean contact to the ball with his right hand during the dunk attempt.
Carter Jr. (CHI) makes contact with Sexton's (CLE) arm and face during his dunk attempt.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Nance Jr.'s (CLE) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Clarkson's (CLE) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
LaVine (CHI) makes marginal contact with Clarkson (CLE) off ball, but doesn't fully extend his arms or affect his ability to maintain position.
Nance Jr. (CLE) moves laterally into LaVine's (CHI) path and affects his SQBR.
Carter Jr. (CHI) firms up during the off ball screen to Clarkson (CLE) and makes marginal contact.
Satoransky (CHI) commits a take foul on Nance Jr. (CLE).
Osman (CLE) moves alongside LaVine's (CHI) body and makes marginal contact that doesn't affect his ability to get into his natural shooting motion.
LaVine (CHI) wraps Sexton (CLE) off ball prior to the release of the inbound pass.
Thompson (CLE) hooks Carter Jr.'s (CHI) waist and dislodges him as he attempts to get to the loose ball.
Porter Jr. (CHI) commits a take foul on Sexton (CLE).
Satoransky (CHI) wraps Love (CLE) prior to the inbound pass.
Porter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Thompson's (CLE) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Sexton (CLE) makes marginal contact with Satoransky (CHI) off ball and he is able to move through it without affecting his SQBR.
Thompson (CLE) makes clean contact to the ball as he defends the pass.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Clarkson (CLE).
